PATTERN SEQ(TYPE_0 v0, TYPE_1 v1, TYPE_2 v2)
FROM synthetic
USING SKIP_TILL_NEXT_MATCH
WHERE 0 <= v0.a1 <= 50 AND 50 <= v0.a2 <= 200 AND 0 <= v1.a1 <= 50 AND 50 <= v1.a2 <= 200 AND 0<= v2.a3 <= 200 AND 200 <= v2.a4 <= 350
WITHIN 2000 units
RETURN COUNT(*)

PATTERN SEQ(TYPE_18 v0, TYPE_2 v1, TYPE_15 v2)
FROM synthetic
USING SKIP_TILL_NEXT_MATCH
WHERE 0 <= v0.a1 <= 50 AND 200 <= v0.a2 <= 350 AND 0 <= v2.a1 <= 50 AND 0 <= v2.a3 <= 200 AND 350 <= v2.a4 <= 500 AND v1.a3 <= v2.a3 AND v0.a1 <= v1.a1 AND v0.a2 <= v2.a2
WITHIN 1000 units
RETURN COUNT(*)

PATTERN SEQ(TYPE_24 v0, TYPE_21 v1, TYPE_20 v2, TYPE_21 v3, TYPE_3 v4)
FROM synthetic
USING SKIP_TILL_ANY_MATCH
WHERE 0 <= v0.a1 <= 50 AND 0 <= v1.a1 <= 50 AND 0 <= v1.a3 <= 200 AND 350 <= v1.a4 <= 500 AND 0 <= v2.a1 <= 50 AND 200 <= v2.a2 <= 350 AND 0 <= v2.a3 <= 200 AND 350 <= v2.a4 <= 500 AND 200 <= v3.a2 <= 350 AND 0 <= v4.a1 <= 50 AND 200 <= v4.a2 <= 350 AND v0.a1 <= v1.a1 AND v3.a1 <= v4.a1
WITHIN 1000 units
RETURN COUNT(*)

PATTERN SEQ(TYPE_2 v0, TYPE_18 v1, TYPE_1 v2, TYPE_17 v3, TYPE_15 v4, TYPE_17 v5)
FROM synthetic
USING SKIP_TILL_ANY_MATCH
WHERE 0 <= v0.a1 <= 50 AND 0 <= v0.a3 <= 200 AND 0 <= v1.a3 <= 200 AND 200 <= v2.a2 <= 350 AND 0 <= v3.a1 <= 50 AND 0 <= v4.a1 <= 50 AND 200 <= v4.a2 <= 350 AND 350 <= v5.a4 <= 500 AND v1.a2 <= v5.a2 AND v0.a3 <= v5.a3 AND v1.a3 <= v2.a3
WITHIN 1000 units
RETURN COUNT(*)
